Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,# Loyalty 忠诚
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 前奏
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-1
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.24,0:00:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你看到我从天上飞过\NYou see me soaring through the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.88,0:00:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我看到你从地上走过\NI see you below as you walk on by
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.56,0:00:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我只要十秒就能清光云层\NI could clear the sky in 10 seconds flat
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.04,0:00:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}厉不厉害\NWell, how about that,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}厉不厉害？\Nwell, how about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.80,0:00:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我可以坐在云上好好放松\NI could be sitting here on a cloud,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.50,0:00:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}看著太阳缓缓下山\Nwatching the sun as it starts to go down
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.40,0:01:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}现在只缺一个人\NThe only thing missing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.04,0:01:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那就是你\Nis you by my side
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 导歌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.52,0:01:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}给我来些自信心\NGive me a smidge of confidence
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.24,0:01:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}给我来点有意义的话\NGive me a speck of something that makes sense
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.16,0:01:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}让我来给你依靠\NGive me an idea of dependency
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.64,0:01:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}让我来展现忠诚心\NGive me a dash of loyalty
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.80,0:01:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}忠诚心\NLoyalty
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 副歌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.04,0:01:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我能给你我孤单的灵魂\NI could save my lonely soul for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.40,0:01:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但我总是感觉不能接受\Nbut the feeling in my heart can't follow through
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.92,0:01:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H40&}不能接受\Ncan't follow through
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.12,0:01:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H40&}不能接受\Ncan't follow through
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.80,0:01:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你可以给我你破碎的心\NYou can give your broken heart to me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.92,0:01:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}因为你知道我会陪著你\N'cause you know that I'll stay with you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.76,0:01:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}所以「忠诚」才是我的座右铭\NThat's why they call me loyalty
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.68,0:01:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}忠诚心\NLoyalty
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-2
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.02,0:02:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}太阳高挂，可却下了雨\NThe sun shines bright, yet the rain pours on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.50,0:02:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}彩虹一下来一下又离开\NRainbows here one minute and then they're gone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.32,0:02:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他们让我想起了你\NThey remind me of me and you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.88,0:02:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你做了什么？\NWhat did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.06,0:02:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我做了什么？\NWhat did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.48,0:02:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你双眼里的决心\NDetermination in those eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.26,0:02:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他们去哪了？已经消失了吗？\NWhere has it gone? Has it said goodbye?
